      "text": "ツアー期間中、いろんなことがあった……\n密度の濃い毎日だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many things happened‚ during the tour…\nEvery day was so full…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4199314594,
      "endTime": 20.2199314594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.4361672878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
