      "text": "そうね……ライブ以外でもいろいろあったわ\n本当にいろいろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… We had a lot of experiences outside of the lives too.\nQuite a lot‚ really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4361672878,
      "endTime": 27.7199314594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.9361672878
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピが全国各地に出没してたって\nSNSでも話題になってたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said Sunny Peace was popping up all over the country‚\nand it became a hot topic on social media.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9361672878,
      "endTime": 34.9065288067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1227646351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "知ってる人も多いと思うけど\n私達、サプライズで全国のファンに会ってきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure many of you already know‚\nbut we've been surprising our fans all over the country.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1227646351,
      "endTime": 41.5931299687,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.8093657971
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いろんな場所に行って\nたっくさんのファンに会えて、楽しかったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We went to various places\nand met so many fans. It was really fun~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.8093657971,
      "endTime": 48.5316332341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.7426991304
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "貴重な話、一杯聞けた……\nみんなの顔を見られて、嬉しかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got to hear‚ so many valuable stories…\nI was so happy‚ to see everyone's faces…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7426991304,
      "endTime": 54.8164632639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0326990923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ライブツアーは今日で終わるけど\n私達の物語はこれからも続いていきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live tour ends today‚\nbut our story will continue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.0326990923,
      "endTime": 61.4300005755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6326990923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しい気持ち……感謝の気持ち……\n一杯の想いを込めて、ステージからみんなに届けるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy feelings… feelings of gratitude…\nI'll deliver all these feelings to you from the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6326990923,
      "endTime": 71.7816790423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livehousemiddle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.9660324257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "だからみんなも声を出して、私達に想いを聞かせて！\n心を繋げて、一緒に歌おう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So everyone‚ raise your voices and let us hear your feelings!\nLet's connect our hearts and sing together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9660324257,
      "endTime": 81.5168029945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
